图片来源：Twitter作者：王博雅琪 本文来源：环球网“ 俄塔社注意到，受新冠肺炎疫情影响，方济各“身体不适”这件事引发了一些媒体猜测。
http: / / space.englishcn.com http: / / www.wenmi5.com "The news that Franciscans are" unwell "as a result of the new crown pneumonia has sparked some media speculation.
梵蒂冈近日还专门采取了一些措施以防止新冠病毒传播，比如在圣彼得广场上，要求信徒之间必须保持一定距离。
The Vatican has recently taken steps to prevent the spread of the virus, such as requiring a certain distance between believers in St. Peter's Square.
”罗马天主教教皇方济各又因“身体不适”取消工作安排。
Roman Catholic Pope Francis has cancelled work plans because he is "unwell."
俄塔社称，方济各3月1日出席传统布道会时宣布，因患感冒自己将无法参加即将到来的传统精神静修周活动。
When Franciscans attended a traditional church service on March 1, he announced that he would not be able to attend the upcoming traditional spiritual retreat because of a cold, Ota said.
据俄塔社描述，宣布这一消息时，方济各还咳嗽了两声。
When the news was announced, Franciscans also coughed twice, according to RTA.
《纽约每日新闻》表示，这是方济各自担任罗马教皇7年以来首次缺席该活动。
The New York Daily News said it was the first time Francis had been absent from the event in seven years as Pope.
3月1日，方济各出席布道会。
On 1 March, Franciscans attended a sermon.
图自美联社“请大家为今晚在（罗马近郊）阿里恰开始的精神静修周祈祷”，“今年，感冒让我无法参加这一活动。
"Please pray for the spiritual retreat that began tonight in Aricha," AP quoted. "This year, the cold has prevented me from taking part.
”俄塔社称，当地时间3月1日，方济各出席传统布道会时宣布了这一消息，期间他还咳嗽了两声。
The news was announced March 1, when Franciscans attended a traditional sermon, during which he coughed twice, Ota said.
不过，方济各同时补充说，自己将在梵蒂冈进行精神静修。
Franciscans, however, added that he would be doing spiritual retreats at the Vatican.
据俄塔社介绍，往常，方济各会与罗马神职人员一同前往罗马近郊参与这一活动。
As usual, Franciscans and Roman clergy went to the suburbs of Rome to take part in the event, Rita said.
这并非方济各首次因“身体不适”取消工作安排。
This is not the first time that Francis has canceled work arrangements because of "physical discomfort."
据美联社此前报道，上周三（26日），方济各身体不适，出现咳嗽和打喷涕的症状。
According to The Associated Press, Franciscans did not feel well last Wednesday, showing symptoms of coughing and sniffling.
第二天，他取消了一场原本与罗马神职人员共同出席的弥撒，并在周五缺席了一场会议。
The next day, he cancelled a mass he had attended with the Roman clergy and was absent from a meeting on Friday.
《纽约每日新闻》评论说，在三天的时间里，方济各缺席了两场原定举行的官方活动，这是这位罗马教皇做出的罕见决定——他从未缺席过这么多活动。
The New York Daily News commented that Franciscans had been absent from two scheduled official events over a three-day period, a rare decision by the Pope - he had never been absent from so many events.
俄塔社注意到，受新冠肺炎疫情影响，方济各“身体不适”这件事引发了一些媒体猜测。
The news agency noted that Franciscans' "ill health," affected by the outbreak of new crown pneumonia, has sparked some media speculation.
梵蒂冈近日还专门采取了一些措施以防止新冠病毒传播，比如在圣彼得广场上，要求信徒之间必须保持一定距离。
The Vatican has recently taken steps to prevent the spread of the virus, such as requiring a certain distance between believers in St. Peter's Square.
梵蒂冈，位于意大利首都罗马西北高地上。
Vatican City located in the Italian capital of Rome northwest highlands.
综合美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）及《欧洲时报》3月1日最新报道，意大利民防局当天宣布，该国累计新冠肺炎确诊病例达1694例，死亡病例34例。
A total of 1,694 confirmed cases of pneumonia and 34 deaths have been reported in Italy, the Civil Defence Bureau (ICD) said on Monday.
目前，意大利成亚洲以外新冠肺炎确诊病例数量最多的国家。
Italy now has the highest number of confirmed cases of pneumonia outside Asia.
